{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867910/extras/fight.gif?t=1736797198\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Sol Apocalypse is a spaceship management and combat game set in a dangerous solar system. Engage in real-time tactical battles and make decisions in multiple storylines. Command your crew and manage the energy consumption of your ship.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Vast, Uncanny, Invaded, and Betrayed. This is our home, Captain. Systema Solaris.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The excitement of first contact with aliens ended when the locust swarm arrived. The political system has collapsed. There are no rumors other than rumors of treason by politicians and oligarchs. Most of the fleet was destroyed by an unexpected attack.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Order of Authority</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">While you were the 4th captain on the Silver Wolf, you found yourself at the top with the deaths of your superiors in a surprise attack. Now your crew and all the rest are counting on you. Arm your ship, prepare for battle, and defeat the enemy to become master of your fate!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867910/extras/gif_laser.gif?t=1736797198\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Asteroid Mining</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Mine asteroids for resources, survive in dark and dangerous tunnels, and manage to return to your ship.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867910/extras/mine.gif?t=1736797198\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867910/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736797198","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867910/page.bg.jpg?t=173679